1
00:01:42,520 --> 00:01:44,880
Liu Qing was originally named Xiang Qing.

2
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:46,560
Her father, Xiang Yue,

3
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:50,120
was once a timber business partner of Liu Jinzhao.

4
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:53,200
The two of them often went deep into the mountains to find timber.

5
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:55,680
Once, they found good wood in a catalpa forest.

6
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:57,680
However, they encountered a python on the way back.

7
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,680
Xiang Yue

8
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,520
unfortunately lost his life.

9
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:03,520
His daughter, Xiang Qing, was fostered in a temple.

10
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:07,440
After Liu Jinzhao logged and sold the catalpa forest,

11
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:08,960
he made a fortune.

12
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:12,200
The first thing he did after getting rich

13
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:15,280
was to go to the temple to bring Xiang Qing back

14
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:17,280
and adopt her as his daughter.

15
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:18,640
Fire!

16
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,760
Fire! Father, why are you in such a hurry?

17
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:21,840
What fire?

18
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,240
The courtyard where Jueming lives

19
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,520
caught fire.

20
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:26,540
Then let's go check it out. Go.

21
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,440
When I just arrived at the courtyard,

22
00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:30,520
I found it was on fire.

23
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,560
Fortunately, the fire was not big.

24
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,360
The fire was put out, and the house was saved.

25
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:35,200
Only this desk was burned down.

26
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:40,720
Did you see clearly

27
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:41,920
who did it?

28
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,480
There are no other clues at present,

29
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:46,410
but I've arranged for others to investigate nearby.

30
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:50,380
Constable Su, the arson suspect has been found.

31
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:51,360
Where is he?

32
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,640
Found by Prefect Chen.

33
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:53,760
The person has been escorted to the government office,

34
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:56,420
waiting for the court session to be questioned.

35
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,920
Return to the government office.

36
00:02:58,920 --> 00:02:59,680
Hold court!

37
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:04,520
Silence.

38
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,960
Who is kneeling before the court?

39
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,000
What crime have you committed?

40
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,600
Confess everything truthfully.

41
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:15,600
Your Honor,

42
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:17,640
my name is Guo Cheng.

43
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:22,720
I make a living transporting goods on the Cao River.

44
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:25,240
Business has been slow these past few days.

45
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:28,440
I saw an empty house nearby,

46
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,200
and I had evil thoughts.

47
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:32,480
When I tried to steal some valuables,

48
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:34,980
I accidentally knocked over a candlestick.

49
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,160
I was so terrified.

50
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,600
I didn't dare to stay,

51
00:03:37,640 --> 00:03:38,880
and ran away.

52
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:40,960
I didn't manage to steal a thing.

53
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:48,000
According to Tang law,

54
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:50,079
attempted theft without obtaining property

55
00:03:50,079 --> 00:03:51,640
is punished with 50 lashes.

56
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,760
You accidentally knocked over the candlestick,

57
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:55,160
started a fire,

58
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,400
and burned the table.

59
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,079
Although unintentional,

60
00:03:58,079 --> 00:03:59,960
you must also bear the responsibility.

61
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,880
According to the laws of the Tang Dynasty,

62
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:04,880
if the damage caused by the fire is minimal,

63
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:07,240
the punishment is 40 days in prison.

64
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,800
Chen You.

65
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:18,760
Come, take the suspect Guo Cheng away.

66
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:20,399
First, give him 50 lashes,

67
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,800
then lock him up in the cell,

68
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,240
and keep him there for 40 days.

69
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,240
Court dismissed.

70
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:27,960
Silence.

71
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:35,000
I sent someone to investigate that Guo Cheng.

72
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:37,240
He is indeed a transport merchant on the Cao River.

73
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,560
Normally, government goods

74
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,890
are transported by him.

75
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:42,720
He definitely skims off a lot.

76
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,800
Someone of his status,

77
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,800
how could he possibly commit theft?

78
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:49,780
And I didn't light a candle when I left the house.

79
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:53,000
There's no need to light a candle to burgle my house during the day.

80
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,860
This Magistrate Chen, he must be hiding something.

81
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,960
I'll have my father investigate Chen You thoroughly.

82
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:00,480
We don't have enough evidence now.

83
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,680
Going there so rashly

84
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:03,320
will easily alert the enemy.

85
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:04,240
Su Lang,

86
00:05:04,640 --> 00:05:06,170
do you have any other clues?

87
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:07,200
I also found out

88
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:09,400
that Father Liu did leave a will.

89
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,560
According to custom,

90
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,960
he invited relatives and prominent people

91
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:13,840
in the neighborhood to be witnesses,

92
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:16,440
and also a minor official from the government.

93
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,400
Father Liu only has

94
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:18,960
Liu Shiqin and Liu Qing.

95
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:21,040
They split the inheritance 70/30.

96
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:22,410
Liu Shiqin gets 70%,

97
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:24,080
and Liu Qing gets 30%.

98
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,480
Could it be

99
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:31,120
that Liu Qing was dissatisfied with the inheritance distribution,

100
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,680
and colluded with Chen You

101
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:35,720
to kill Liu Shiqin while she was severely injured?

102
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,320
These are all speculations.

103
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:40,120
We still have no way to find out

104
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:42,680
the relationship between Sun Wenhuai and Liu Shiqin.

105
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,400
If the table hadn't been burned,

106
00:05:44,400 --> 00:05:46,360
there might still be some hope.

107
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:54,880
Back then,

108
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:57,580
when we caught Sun Wenhuai and put him in prison,

109
00:05:58,520 --> 00:06:01,920
he once faked a stomachache and escaped.

110
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,640
He really did run away.

111
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,920
When we caught him again,

112
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,560
Get in.

113
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:16,440
I never intended to escape.

114
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:20,400
You caught me on my way back.

115
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,400
Do you think I'd believe you?

116
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:25,060
Still trying to make excuses.

117
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:30,120
I've written down exactly what happened.

118
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,640
Once he sees it,

119
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:34,500
he will definitely figure something out for me.

120
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:43,159
I didn't understand what he meant back then.

121
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:47,320
But thinking back on it now,

122
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:49,440
his prison break that time

123
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:53,840
was just to deliver the suicide note to you.

124
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:55,480
The antique shop where you sold the desk,

125
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,040
what was its name?

126
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,680
Ruixiang Antique Shop

127
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,930
is still open today.

128
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:03,480
He did come here back then.

129
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:06,640
It was probably early afternoon.

130
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,800
He ran over wearing a prison uniform.

131
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,960
So I remember it very well.

132
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,820
Shopkeeper! Shopkeeper!

133
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:16,800
A few days ago,

134
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:18,720
did a boy surnamed Sun

135
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:21,400
sell all his furniture here?

136
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,240
Was there a brown desk?

137
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:27,600
Where is it now?

138
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:56,760
Every now and then,

139
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:59,040
he would repeatedly open the secret compartment to check.

140
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,040
After a long while,

141
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,560
his eyes were filled with disappointment.

142
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,840
He still asked me,

143
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:06,120
saying if any new letters appeared in the secret compartment,

144
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:08,450
I should give them to his younger brother.

145
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:11,960
How could new letters possibly appear in this secret compartment?

146
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,320
He might have been

147
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:15,330
provoked by something at the time,

148
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,200
and wasn't in his right mind.

149
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:23,440
Is it possible that

150
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:26,930
Sun Wenhuai put the blood letter in the secret compartment,

151
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:30,640
so it appeared in your desk?

152
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:32,679
But Chen You burned the desk,

153
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:34,640
so the blood letter was gone.

154
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:36,440
If so,

155
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:42,400
is the suicide note Sun Wenhuai put in the secret compartment back then still there?

156
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:43,080
Yes.

157
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:44,800
I took it out after he left.

158
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:47,440
I thought he would come back.

159
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,330
What are you looking at?

160
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,600
Can you read it?

161
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:20,020
Is this your brother's handwriting?

162
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:21,160
Yes.

163
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:23,400
It's my brother's handwriting.

164
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:28,400
I first met Liu Shiqin at the Lotus Pond Poetry Gathering.

165
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:36,320
I first met Liu Shiqin at the Lotus Pond Poetry Gathering.

166
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:38,240
She has exceptional zither skills

167
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,600
and a sweet smile.

168
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:43,280
That day, everyone drew the first line of a couplet.

169
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:46,900
Snow covers the green mountains,

170
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:51,280
cold shadows and lonely peaks are hard to paint.

171
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:55,480
The green water ripples.

172
00:09:56,160 --> 00:10:00,520
Fine ripples and shallow waves easily form a poem.

173
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:17,160
The first line of the couplet I drew

174
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:19,320
happens to be by Liu Shiqin.

175
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:22,400
I thought hard to come up with the second line,

176
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:24,880
but felt it wasn't profound enough,

177
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:27,560
so I put the couplet in the drawer.

178
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:31,820
I wanted to use the couplet to ask Liu Shiqin for advice,

179
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:34,520
but I didn't know how to bring it up.

180
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,220
She misunderstood me,

181
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:38,600
and called a constable to scold me.

182
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:42,160
I expressed my affection for Liu Shiqin,

183
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:44,760
but was insulted by the officer.

184
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:46,800
I wanted to clear up the misunderstanding,

185
00:10:46,800 --> 00:10:48,680
so I went to find Liu Shiqin again.

186
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:52,370
I saw her arguing with the owner at the eatery.

187
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:54,800
I wanted to step forward and reason for her.

188
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:57,420
But Liu Shiqin turned and ran when she saw me.

189
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:59,100
I hurriedly chased after her.

190
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:01,040
The eatery has two floors.

191
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:04,040
She accidentally fell down while going down the stairs.

192
00:11:04,040 --> 00:11:06,080
I did not touch Liu Shiqin at all.

193
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:11,520
Constable Su Yu'an recklessly concluded

194
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:14,520
that I pushed her downstairs, causing her injuries.

195
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:16,680
Su Yu'an made this false conclusion,

196
00:11:16,920 --> 00:11:20,840
determining that I am directly responsible for Liu Shiqin's injuries.

197
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:24,240
According to Tang law, the case entered the recovery period.

198
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:27,480
Unexpectedly, during the recovery period,

199
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:29,680
Liu Shiqin unfortunately died.

200
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:32,160
I was then considered a murderer.

201
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:34,360
I am completely innocent.

202
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:38,800
Su Yu'an is the chief culprit who framed me.

203
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,440
I implore the court to see the truth.

204
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,800
Liu Shiqin and I

205
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:57,200
have known each other since childhood.

206
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:00,000
You could say

207
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:03,320
I watched her grow up.

208
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:10,280
When I learned

209
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:12,800
that Liu Shiqin was injured,

210
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:15,320
I concluded that

211
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:18,720
Sun Wenhuai approached her just to bully her

212
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:21,360
and did it.

213
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,320
Back then,

214
00:12:26,520 --> 00:12:29,240
I was young and hot-blooded,

215
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:32,080
so I insisted that

216
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:36,960
Sun Wenhuai pushed Liu Shiqin down the stairs.

217
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:42,960
I originally just wanted to punish Sun Wenhuai a little

218
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:45,680
so he wouldn't harass Liu Shiqin anymore.

219
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:48,000
But I never expected

220
00:12:48,760 --> 00:12:49,880
that Liu Shiqin

221
00:12:51,640 --> 00:12:53,600
would pass away within

222
00:12:55,720 --> 00:12:57,120
the period of liability.

223
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:04,720
What's done is done.

224
00:13:04,760 --> 00:13:06,620
Blaming yourself is useless now.

225
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:08,320
If the truth can be revealed,

226
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:11,450
it will surely comfort Sun Wenhuai's soul in heaven.

227
00:13:25,800 --> 00:13:27,280
The letter mentioned that

228
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:30,240
when Sun Wenhuai found Liu Shiqin,

229
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:33,040
he saw her arguing with the shopkeeper.

230
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:37,400
Mr. Su.

231
00:13:38,280 --> 00:13:40,000
We need to understand

232
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:42,040
why they were arguing.

233
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,240
This shop

234
00:13:48,040 --> 00:13:50,000
is still there today.

235
00:13:56,040 --> 00:13:57,170
Let's go take a look.

236
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:01,360
Come on, boss.

237
00:14:01,560 --> 00:14:03,290
Tell us what happened that day.

238
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:11,080
She actually

239
00:14:11,680 --> 00:14:13,360
argued with me that day.

240
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:16,280
Then she fell down the stairs.

241
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:19,880
I was actually gloating a bit at the time.

242
00:14:19,920 --> 00:14:22,360
I didn't expect her to die from the fall.

243
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:24,800
Why did you argue with her?

244
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:29,480
Our shop has always delivered food to her family.

245
00:14:29,920 --> 00:14:32,440
That day, she suddenly came to confront me.

246
00:14:32,680 --> 00:14:35,520
Boss, why was my father's food changed?

247
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:36,960
What food?

248
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:38,280
Look here.

249
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:40,840
Your ledger clearly states

250
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:42,880
that my father's food was changed to white rice and white flour.

251
00:14:42,880 --> 00:14:43,920
He can't eat that.

252
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,200
He can only eat coarse grains.

253
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:46,160
Look,

254
00:14:46,560 --> 00:14:49,040
you guys must have notified us to change it.

255
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:50,920
When did I notify you?

256
00:14:51,160 --> 00:14:52,400
No, you...

257
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:54,880
We wouldn't change it without your notification.

258
00:14:54,880 --> 00:14:56,640
I have things to do. I'll go first.

259
00:14:56,640 --> 00:14:59,040
I remembered it wrong at the time.

260
00:14:59,080 --> 00:15:01,080
I said she was the one who changed it.

261
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:03,000
Then we started arguing.

262
00:15:07,560 --> 00:15:08,920
Who wanted to change it?

263
00:15:11,760 --> 00:15:14,440
It was her sister, Liu Qing.

264
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:21,920
Liu Qing... She is indeed a suspect.

265
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:25,600
Mr. Su,

266
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:28,320
where is the master's grave?

267
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:33,360
I'll take you to find it.

268
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:35,760
Let's go.

269
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:46,440
Slow down.

270
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:55,320
Master Wang,

271
00:15:55,920 --> 00:15:59,080
it is truly fate that we met.

272
00:15:59,520 --> 00:16:02,480
I am here now to find out the truth of your death.

273
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:05,240
So I have to bring you out now.

274
00:16:05,280 --> 00:16:06,800
Please don't blame me.

275
00:16:07,800 --> 00:16:09,040
But don't worry.

276
00:16:09,160 --> 00:16:11,160
When everything is cleared up,

277
00:16:11,560 --> 00:16:12,840
I will put you back.

278
00:16:13,120 --> 00:16:14,160
I have my reasons.

279
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:16,530
Please don't blame me. Dad, go take a look.

280
00:16:17,800 --> 00:16:18,360
You scared me to death.

281
00:16:18,360 --> 00:16:20,200
I thought Master Wang was here.

282
00:16:20,320 --> 00:16:20,840
Why are you so timid?

283
00:16:20,840 --> 00:16:22,040
What do you mean?

284
00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:23,320
Are you trying to invite Master Wang out

285
00:16:23,320 --> 00:16:24,600
and put your dad in?

286
00:16:24,640 --> 00:16:26,100
How could I bear to do that?

287
00:16:26,320 --> 00:16:27,080
Let's go.

288
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:32,200
The bones are still intact.

289
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:34,460
Nothing inside has been touched, right?

290
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:38,060
Okay, let's ask Miss Li to take another look.

291
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:40,320
Miss Li.

292
00:16:40,680 --> 00:16:41,800
Coroner Li.

293
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:42,880
It's your turn.

294
00:16:42,920 --> 00:16:43,320
Go ahead.

295
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:45,050
We don't understand it anyway.

296
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:59,120
Is there something wrong with this corpse?

297
00:17:00,160 --> 00:17:01,480
For those who die of a stroke,

298
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:06,339
the cause of death is usually cerebral congestion or phlegm blocking the collaterals.

299
00:17:06,359 --> 00:17:09,920
Their bones wouldn't have such black discoloration.

300
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:12,480
For those who are poisoned,

301
00:17:12,520 --> 00:17:14,040
once the poison enters the body,

302
00:17:14,040 --> 00:17:15,280
it circulates

303
00:17:15,319 --> 00:17:17,960
along with Qi and blood.

304
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:22,640
The throat is a vital passage for eating and breathing.

305
00:17:22,960 --> 00:17:24,880
Poison easily accumulates there,

306
00:17:24,880 --> 00:17:26,800
causing the bones to show abnormal colors.

307
00:17:26,800 --> 00:17:28,130
Therefore, we can infer

308
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:32,000
that the advisor didn't die of the rumored illness,

309
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:33,880
but was poisoned.

310
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:34,960
Poisoned?

311
00:17:35,000 --> 00:17:35,600
Yeah.

312
00:17:36,360 --> 00:17:38,440
I knew there was something wrong with this advisor.

313
00:17:38,440 --> 00:17:39,720
Died of poisoning.

314
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:41,960
That explains everything.

315
00:17:42,520 --> 00:17:45,920
Back then, they used Sun Wenhuai as a scapegoat

316
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:47,690
and then silenced the advisor.

317
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:51,920
Now, Guo Cheng in prison should be the new scapegoat.

318
00:17:52,320 --> 00:17:55,320
Chen You is very likely to target him.

319
00:17:55,360 --> 00:17:59,880
The young lady is embroidering a sachet in her room.

320
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:00,960
Time to eat.

321
00:18:01,040 --> 00:18:02,160
Oh, time to eat.

322
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:04,360
I'm starving to death.

323
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:08,290
There are chicken legs.

324
00:18:18,360 --> 00:18:19,680
Let me go.

325
00:18:20,360 --> 00:18:21,680
Let me go.

326
00:18:29,840 --> 00:18:31,170
You are not fated to die.

327
00:18:31,440 --> 00:18:33,000
Thank God.

328
00:18:43,560 --> 00:18:44,840
Madam, they are looking for you.

329
00:18:44,840 --> 00:18:45,840
You may leave.

330
00:18:52,880 --> 00:18:53,720
Liu Qing.

331
00:18:55,120 --> 00:18:57,760
Liu Jinzhao suffered from diabetes.

332
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:59,160
Did you know that?

333
00:19:01,600 --> 00:19:02,600
I did.

334
00:19:03,520 --> 00:19:05,320
Dr. Wang from Baicao Clinic said

335
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:07,960
that in the late stages of Liu Jinzhao's illness,

336
00:19:07,960 --> 00:19:10,080
he was completely blind and had lost his sense of taste.

337
00:19:10,080 --> 00:19:13,480
He couldn't even tell the sugar content of his daily food.

338
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:15,920
The food shop owner said

339
00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:18,280
that you took the coarse grains Liu Shiqin had been ordering.

340
00:19:18,280 --> 00:19:21,210
Replaced with fine, sweetened white rice and flour.

341
00:19:22,960 --> 00:19:26,960
For a patient with diabetes, eating this would rapidly worsen their condition.

342
00:19:26,960 --> 00:19:28,320
Did you know that?

343
00:19:31,360 --> 00:19:32,480
I didn't.

344
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:39,000
I imagine back then,

345
00:19:39,600 --> 00:19:41,680
you probably said the same thing.

346
00:19:47,240 --> 00:19:49,840
We've both heard the doctor's orders.

347
00:19:50,440 --> 00:19:52,680
For a patient with diabetes,

348
00:19:52,840 --> 00:19:55,400
eating sweetened white rice and flour

349
00:19:55,560 --> 00:19:58,000
will rapidly worsen their condition.

350
00:19:58,320 --> 00:20:00,360
There is no way you didn't know this.

351
00:20:02,080 --> 00:20:05,640
And you were specifically in charge of father's diet.

352
00:20:06,320 --> 00:20:08,400
Only you could have tampered with it.

353
00:20:10,880 --> 00:20:12,320
Father made a will.

354
00:20:13,680 --> 00:20:15,000
You got a small share,

355
00:20:15,760 --> 00:20:17,360
so you treated him like this.

356
00:20:28,960 --> 00:20:30,720
Since you know everything,

357
00:20:31,280 --> 00:20:32,720
if you die,

358
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:35,000
wouldn't I get an even bigger share?

359
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:42,800
Don't mention your father to me.

360
00:20:42,800 --> 00:20:44,730
He is the enemy of our Xiang family.

361
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:47,080
Since you found out,

362
00:20:47,240 --> 00:20:48,500
you can't live either.

363
00:20:51,600 --> 00:20:52,880
What are you waiting for?

364
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:55,080
If she doesn't die, we'll be in trouble.

365
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:57,920
Hold her down.

366
00:21:02,280 --> 00:21:03,600
Quick, grab her wound.

367
00:21:27,840 --> 00:21:28,960
What's that sound?

368
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:34,440
Yes. It was a mouse.

369
00:21:36,760 --> 00:21:38,120
Where is Shiqin?

370
00:21:38,360 --> 00:21:41,800
She's already asleep.

371
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:44,440
Buy some rat poison.

372
00:21:44,840 --> 00:21:46,440
Don't let the mice

373
00:21:46,480 --> 00:21:50,240
keep us awake all day long.

374
00:21:50,440 --> 00:21:53,080
As long as the mice are gone,

375
00:21:53,120 --> 00:21:55,480
everything will be fine.

376
00:21:59,600 --> 00:22:03,400
You and Chen You killed Liu Shiqin,

377
00:22:04,040 --> 00:22:05,570
colluded with the advisor,

378
00:22:06,280 --> 00:22:10,080
and tampered with Liu Shiqin's autopsy report written by Qin Boyan.

379
00:22:10,200 --> 00:22:11,860
To eliminate future trouble,

380
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:13,760
you poisoned the advisor.

381
00:22:14,520 --> 00:22:16,850
I opened the coffin and examined his body.

382
00:22:17,320 --> 00:22:19,440
There are indeed signs of poisoning.

383
00:22:21,320 --> 00:22:22,780
It is not hard to figure out

384
00:22:23,120 --> 00:22:26,360
if the advisor shared a meal with you before he died.

385
00:22:27,640 --> 00:22:29,170
What else do you have to say?

386
00:22:49,760 --> 00:22:52,120
My father, Xiang Yue,

387
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:56,600
went to the deep mountains with Liu Jinzhao to find timber.

388
00:22:57,480 --> 00:23:00,400
On the way back, they encountered a python,

389
00:23:01,680 --> 00:23:05,440
and my father unfortunately died.

390
00:23:07,040 --> 00:23:09,200
After Liu Jinzhao adopted me,

391
00:23:09,640 --> 00:23:11,080
one night when I woke up,

392
00:23:12,280 --> 00:23:14,520
I heard him talking in his sleep.

393
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:23,560
Brother Xiang,

394
00:23:23,920 --> 00:23:25,520
I am sorry.

395
00:23:26,080 --> 00:23:27,640
I am so sorry.

396
00:23:32,360 --> 00:23:33,760
Don't blame me.

397
00:23:34,600 --> 00:23:37,640
I didn't mean to push you into the snake pit.

398
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:39,360
I was too scared.

399
00:23:39,720 --> 00:23:41,120
Please don't blame me.

400
00:23:48,440 --> 00:23:50,680
The wealth earned by the Liu family

401
00:23:51,800 --> 00:23:54,520
should have belonged to my Xiang family.

402
00:23:57,960 --> 00:23:59,080
It should have

403
00:24:02,760 --> 00:24:04,760
belonged to my father.

404
00:24:07,640 --> 00:24:10,720
Why do they get to live so well?

405
00:24:11,280 --> 00:24:12,800
Why?

406
00:24:25,720 --> 00:24:26,480
Get in.

407
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:34,160
What are you doing?

408
00:24:34,480 --> 00:24:37,560
Lord Chen, you have quite a lot of nice things.

409
00:24:38,080 --> 00:24:39,760
Come, tell him

410
00:24:39,800 --> 00:24:41,730
why we came to find Lord Chen today.

411
00:24:42,440 --> 00:24:44,520
It was the magistrate who ordered me to strangle Guo Cheng

412
00:24:44,520 --> 00:24:46,520
and fake his suicide to escape punishment.

413
00:24:46,520 --> 00:24:47,320
Chen You,

414
00:24:47,560 --> 00:24:48,680
you liar!

415
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:50,860
You told me that

416
00:24:51,120 --> 00:24:54,920
if I confessed, I'd get all government transport contracts for the next three years,

417
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:57,120
but now you want to silence me by killing me!

418
00:24:57,120 --> 00:24:58,480
You are making false accusations!

419
00:24:58,480 --> 00:25:00,120
What proof do you two have?

420
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:02,000
Come! Take them all away!

421
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:06,040
Where is everyone? Guards!

422
00:25:10,120 --> 00:25:11,040
Lord Li.

423
00:25:12,640 --> 00:25:14,600
Lord Li, listen to my explanation.

424
00:25:14,640 --> 00:25:16,570
There is a misunderstanding here.

425
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:17,760
Liu Qing,

426
00:25:17,960 --> 00:25:18,840
bring him in.

427
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:37,040
Chen You.

428
00:25:38,080 --> 00:25:39,480
Magistrate Chen.

429
00:25:40,480 --> 00:25:43,440
What else do you have to say now?

430
00:25:46,840 --> 00:25:47,600
Guards,

431
00:25:47,840 --> 00:25:49,120
take them all away.

432
00:25:54,880 --> 00:25:55,520
Move.

433
00:25:58,960 --> 00:26:00,120
Congratulations, Mr. Li,

434
00:26:00,120 --> 00:26:01,850
on solving another major case.

435
00:26:02,680 --> 00:26:04,680
It's all thanks to you.

436
00:27:42,400 --> 00:27:44,080
To think of using a desk

437
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:46,810
to communicate from beyond the grave,

438
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:48,840
only you could do that.

439
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:50,600
Elder Su.

440
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:52,720
What do you mean?

441
00:27:57,080 --> 00:27:58,880
Do you really think I'd believe

442
00:27:58,920 --> 00:28:02,560
that the dead Sun Wenhuai was writing to me?

443
00:28:51,720 --> 00:28:53,600
How did you know it was me?

